    <li>Surgical site infection. Prevention and treatment of surgical site infection. NICE guideline. London (UK): National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2008 Oct. 28 p. (Clinical guideline; no. 74). Available from the <a href="/web/20180713072328/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=13416&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=http%3a%2f%2fwww.nice.org.uk%2fGuidance%2fCG74%2fNiceGuidance%2fpdf%2fEnglish" title="NICE Web site">National Institute for Health and Clinical Excellence (NICE) Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713072328im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
