    <li>CG74: surgical site infection. Surveillance review decision, September 2014. London (UK): National Institute for Clinical Excellence (NICE); 2014 Sep. 117 p. Available from the <a href="/web/20180713072328/https://www.guideline.gov/Home/Disclaimer?id=13416&amp;contentType=summary&amp;redirect=https%3a%2f%2fwww.nice.org.uk%2fguidance%2fCG74%2fdocuments%2fsurgical-site-infection-surveillance-review-document2" title="NICE Web site">NICE Web site</a>&nbsp;<img alt="External Web Site Policy" src="/web/20180713072328im_/https://www.guideline.gov/UI/images/icon_externallink.gif"/>. </li>
